Time documentation
==================

Documentation about the time settings and how it is set

Changing the timezone
---------------------

This has been tested on `Arch Linux`_.

Find the timezone file you want in ``/usr/share/zoneinfo``. Then copy it to
``/etc/localtime``.

To make the change permanent, change the timezone path in ``/etc/rc.conf``

.. _Arch Linux: http://www.archlinux.org/
